  "prompt": "What is Rapportive's business model?",
  "response": "Rapportive was a browser extension and email plugin that provided social media information about email contacts directly within Gmail. Its business model was primarily based on providing professional insights about email senders. LinkedIn ultimately acquired Rapportive in 2012, integrating its technology into LinkedIn's own products. After the acquisition, the standalone Rapportive service was discontinued.",
